{"tid":1327604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 學生動源突然四處邀請中學生團體星期五圍政總","createTime":"2019-07-17T16:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T19:18:16.000Z","uid":61876,"like":6,"dislike":424,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"873d7e2b537dfc240a35e7de05f965f2023b1995","tid":1327604,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"你好，我哋學生動源計劃喺星期五下午四點號召中學生前往政府總部加入政府所舉辦嘅中學生會議，希望邀請你哋到時一齊前往政府總部加入政府閉門會議。<br />\n<br />\n我哋進入政府加入會議將會有兩個前設：<br />\n1.容許所有到場中學生入內參與<br />\n2.容許記者進入會議場地進行採訪<br />\n<br />\n如政府未能答應以上兩項要求我哋將唔會加入會議。<br />\n<br />\n敬覆<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月17號<br />\n學生動源<br />\n<br />\n唔係應該拒絕所有中學生去開會咩<br />\n費事俾政府話聽咗民意<br />\n<br />\n咁樣嘅話佢哋有少少前言不對後語一開始又話點都唔好做"},{"pid":"54410e57f90d22e31fc642d0a83018e6b10f9e21","tid":1327604,"uid":10905,"like":283,"dislike":0,"score":283,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"屌搞咩呀 講真大學生都未必代表到啦<br />\n搵中學生參觀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b308dc377958eb9912ff080590dc83109c8fbb51","tid":1327604,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"萬一林鄭真係肯傾咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd4a6385a8482789f723f0db4f66021bbfee273","tid":1327604,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd0caf8cd843fe2cfb54f48f50fe780b9674a21b","tid":1327604,"uid":139509,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都廢事派"},{"pid":"298ca94c797149fe8b1fcb6443d0cfc1f18c926a","tid":1327604,"uid":151057,"like":194,"dislike":1,"score":193,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"唔好咁蠢俾人當工具<br />\n開完就話傾好咗<br />\n連累成個運動"},{"pid":"4c4160b441307297c5657f119283df881eb67e67","tid":1327604,"uid":151057,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:08:32.00